[37;44m  The Screen  [33;40m
 
 Once you begin play, three rows of 7 cards will be presented.

  [47;31mÚÄÄÄÄÄ¿[33;40m             The cards which are unturned are                 [47;31mÚÄÄÄÄÄ¿[33;40m
